{"tid":501588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國出口轉內銷，荒誕的歷史】","createTime":"2017-12-17T04:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T09:15:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c86bfea4e88ae003cfbb3b2a0a42addd6ebd57bf","tid":501588,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T04:24:12.000Z","msg":"六七十年代，許多香港人郵寄食物回大陸，接濟鄉間饑荒的親友，這是上一輩港人的集體回憶。然而，這些郵寄回鄉的食物究竟從哪裡來？卻是來自餓殍遍野的中國大陸。British Pathe這段影片，記錄了1961年「紅色中國」在大饑荒、許多人饑餓至死的時期，仍然出口大量食物賺外匯。而香港人卻真金白銀買食物寄回鄉，名副其實「出口轉內銷」。<br />\n<br />\n這不是抹黑，曾身在體制內的新華社資深記者楊繼繩，曾走訪全國調查，寫成紀實文學作品《墓碑》，還原六十年代大饑荒的歷史；其中，提到當年中國政府在糧食政策上，「對農民見死不救，繼續高徵購，繼續出口」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/122408_25def0e89917d6f38c80624dcdbfc6bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F122408_25def0e89917d6f38c80624dcdbfc6bf.jpg&h=00364365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=1932525716774797&amp;id=620177918009590\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1932525716774797%26id%3D620177918009590&d=C9rODD4zZtdGQ3sn10KX32Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=477b7f51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=1932525716774797&amp;id=620177918009590</a>"},{"pid":"1d04ad0f796dee91fcaf4e566c79bb804d5c9cd3","tid":501588,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8df5b7eef4a0a1210c4caa76b05f1af2c96538a","tid":501588,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83eb1e017b2cabf8d42c8a7f5587dd479a0bdbd","tid":501588,"uid":44105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"<